|
* Tariff sentences
* Sentence must be proportionate to the crime
|-
|[[Deterrence (legal)|Deterrence]]
|
* To the individual&nbsp;– the individual is deterred through fear of further punishment.
* To the general public&nbsp;– Potential offenders warned as to likely punishment
|
* Prison Sentence
* Heavy Fine
* Long sentence as an example to others
|-
|[[Rehabilitation (penology)|Rehabilitation]]
|To reform the offender's behavior
|
* Individualized sentences
* Community service orders
* moral education
